videos.headline: Melrose: Refs let the Bruins and Blues play in Game 4
videos.description: Barry Melrose describes the physicality that took place between the Blues and Bruins in Game 4 and how the officials were letting them play through it.

videos.headline: Cassidy unsure if Chara will play in Game 5
videos.description: Bruins coach Bruce Cassidy says he doesn't know if Zdeno Chara will play in Game 5 after he took a puck to the face.
